WEBVTT

00:00.679 --> 00:02.311
Previously on The Following...

00:02.675 --> 00:05.716
Serial killer Joe Carroll
has escaped from prison.

00:05.851 --> 00:07.051
Get some help now!

00:07.164 --> 00:09.213
Ryan, I know
things didn't end well with the Bureau,

00:09.327 --> 00:10.435
but you caught Carroll.

00:10.537 --> 00:11.662
No one knows him like you do.

00:11.751 --> 00:12.865
I'm not an agent anymore.

00:12.977 --> 00:14.493
He cut out his victims' eyes as a nod

00:14.618 --> 00:15.966
to his favorite works of Poe.

00:16.072 --> 00:18.013
He didn't just
eviscerate 14 female students.

00:18.123 --> 00:19.051
He was making art.

00:19.176 --> 00:20.581
Sarah was his unfinished work.

00:20.678 --> 00:21.840
He wanted to get the ending right.

00:21.953 --> 00:24.992
The point of Sarah's death was for you.

00:25.101 --> 00:26.139
He's finding people.

00:26.252 --> 00:27.405
They're his followers.

00:27.514 --> 00:28.853
Prison guard,
gay neighbors--

00:28.957 --> 00:30.913
how do they figure into your new plot?

00:31.011 --> 00:31.939
We know about the cult.

00:32.040 --> 00:33.978
I like to think of them as my friends.

00:34.070 --> 00:35.502
So what's my sequel about, Joe?

00:35.604 --> 00:37.019
We're gonna write this together, Ryan,

00:37.126 --> 00:39.430
even though you slept with my wife.

00:39.527 --> 00:40.528
Did she show you the letter?

00:40.635 --> 00:41.645
- How does he know?
- He doesn't.

00:41.758 --> 00:42.725
No one need to know about this.

00:42.836 --> 00:44.798
- Mom, what's going on?
- Yeah.

00:44.960 --> 00:46.049
It's dad, isn't it?

00:46.158 --> 00:47.751
- I didn't know what to say.
- Oh, honey.

00:47.875 --> 00:49.725
If this book ends with
anything other than your death,

00:49.837 --> 00:51.527
you better plan on a rewrite.

00:51.668 --> 00:52.871
Aah! Aah!

00:52.969 --> 00:53.934
Joey? Where is he?

00:54.036 --> 00:55.936
Joey! Joey, honey,
where are you?

00:56.042 --> 00:58.144
Where's Denise?
Where's my son?!

00:59.355 --> 01:01.101
Sorry. Didn't mean
to scare you.

01:01.351 --> 01:02.873
Is everything ok?

01:02.973 --> 01:04.289
Extra patrol this evening.

01:04.411 --> 01:05.609
I thought they caught him.

01:05.703 --> 01:06.674
I saw it on the news.

01:06.808 --> 01:07.712
Still, mind if I look around,

01:07.814 --> 01:08.857
check your doors and windows?

01:08.963 --> 01:10.194
Sure.

01:12.525 --> 01:13.717
Come on in.

01:14.043 --> 01:15.803
I think everyone's asleep.

01:16.142 --> 01:18.434
_

01:18.541 --> 01:20.269
Why don't we start upstairs?

01:25.499 --> 01:26.761
Do you want me to wake everyone?

01:26.894 --> 01:28.710
No. We don't want
to do that.

01:28.812 --> 01:31.055
Let's start with the room on the end.

01:31.293 --> 01:32.558
Ok.

01:39.758 --> 01:41.933
This is Jesse's room. She's out.

01:42.037 --> 01:45.246
Yes. Jesse's room.
I know.

01:47.406 --> 01:49.246
I've studied this house a lot.

