02:00.731 --> 02:02.190
What is that?

02:02.999 --> 02:05.117
I threw this up here earlier.

02:05.988 --> 02:07.586
It's my kit.

02:08.108 --> 02:11.304
It's important to have the right tools.

02:14.487 --> 02:16.908
I've been planning
this for a long time.

